The paper deals with computer vision and scene understanding, which are core topics in the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also involves geometry recovery, which falls under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. The use of RGB-D images suggests that robotics (cs.RO) could be another relevant sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for segmentation and modeling, which could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
